# RoboLedger V5.2.28: UI Scaling & Performance Optimization

This update delivers a significant visibility boost and a performance overhaul for the core island stack.

## 📏 20% Visibility Boost
The top 3 command cards have been scaled up for better ergonomics and a more premium feel.
- [x] **Command Scale**: Header, Action Bar, and Switcher Bar increased in height and font-size by ~20%.
- [x] **Expanded Island**: The total stack max-width expanded from **1166px to 1400px**, giving your data room to breathe.
- [x] **High-Fidelity Text**: All fonts scaled proportionally (e.g., 11px to 13px, 13px to 15px) for maximum readability.

## ⚡ High-Performance Defaulting
The account switcher has been streamlined to eliminate "ALL" view bloat.
- [x] **Individual Focus**: The system now defaults to the first available individual account ledger on load, ensuring near-instant grid rendering.
- [x] **Exploration on Demand**: The unified "ALL" view remains available as an explicit toggle for when you need the full picture.

## 📐 Header Fidelity (V5.2.27)
- [x] **Sharper Dividers**: Column dividers in the header are now **80% white**, creating distinct vertical silos against the rainbow.
- [x] **Uniform Alignment**: Every column title (Ref#, Source, Date, etc.) is now perfectly **left-aligned** for a clean, structured finish.

